### HTTP Test Requests for A2A Spring Demo
### Using jsonrpc4j for proper JSON-RPC 2.0 dispatching
### No switch-case - annotation-based method routing

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Agent Card (Discovery)
GET http://localhost:8080/.well-known/agent-card.json
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Send Weather Task (JSON-RPC)
POST http://localhost:8080/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "req-001",
  "method": "tasks/send",
  "params": {
    "id": "task-001",
    "message": {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "What's the weather in London?"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}

###

